nodes.text: Uda-Khalid's headquarters were in a temple on a jungle part of an unknown planet or moon. It was protected by numerous guards, including a Gotal guard, and was run by Uda-Khalid, a murderous dictator. However, Jedi Master Mace Windu came to the temple one time, and ended up killing Uda-Khalid. What happened to the temple and headquarters afterward is unknown.
